trans-unit.source: The element associated with this automation peer.
The automation peer that is associated with the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControlGroup" /> that holds the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" />.
trans-unit.target: Der Automatisierungspeer für die <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControlGroup" />-Klasse, die die <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" />-Klasse enthält.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" /> class.

Gets the control type for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Ruft den Steuerelementtyp für das <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> ab, das diesem <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" /> zugeordnet ist.

trans-unit.source: Gets the class name of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Ruft den Klassennamen der <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> ab, der diesem <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" /> zugeordnet ist.

trans-unit.source: The class name of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Der Klassenname des <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" />, das diesem <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" /> zugeordnet ist.

trans-unit.source: A value enumeration that specifies the control pattern.
trans-unit.target: Ein Enumerationswert, der den Befehlstyp angibt.

trans-unit.source: Gets the control pattern for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> that is associated with the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Ruft das Steuerelementmuster für das <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonControl" /> ab, das diesem <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonControlDataAutomationPeer" /> zugeordnet ist.

trans-unit.source: An object that supports the control pattern if <paramref name="patternInterface" /> is the <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.SynchronizedInput" /> value; otherwise, <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Ein Objekt, das das Steuerelementmuster unterstützt, wenn <paramref name="patternInterface" /> der <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.SynchronizedInput" />-Wert ist; andernfalls <see langword="null" />.
